'''湯姆·賴斯'''（Hugh Thompson "Tom" Rice Jr.；{{bd|1957年|8月4日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位政治人物。他是現任南卡羅來納州第7選舉區的美國眾議院議員，在2012年11月當選。他是一位保守派共和黨人，支持生命權運動<ref name="Tom Rice: Inexperience could be a good thing.">{{cite news|last=Jones|first=Steve|title=Tom Rice: Inexperience could be a good thing.|url=http://www.myrtlebeachonline.com/2012/11/03/3151793/tom-rice-inexperience-could-be.html|accessdate=November 7, 2012|newspaper=The Sun News|date=November 3, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130119025941/http://www.myrtlebeachonline.com/2012/11/03/3151793/tom-rice-inexperience-could-be.html|archive-date=2013-01-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Horry County Chair seat empty Dec. 31, filing opens mid-January">{{cite web|last=Hinnant|first=Lauren|title=Horry County Chair seat empty Dec. 31, filing opens mid-January|url=http://www2.wbtw.com/news/grand-strand-wbtw/2012/dec/19/horry-county-chair-seat-empty-dec-31-filing-opens-ar-5197919/|publisher=WBTW News 13|accessdate=December 19, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130209123829/http://www2.wbtw.com/news/grand-strand-wbtw/2012/dec/19/horry-county-chair-seat-empty-dec-31-filing-opens-ar-5197919/|archivedate=2013年2月9日}}</ref>。2014年，他成功獲得連任<ref name="Rep. Tom Rice declared victor in bid for 7th District">{{cite web|last1=Jones|first1=Steve|title=Rep. Tom Rice declared victor in bid for 7th District|url=http://www.myrtlebeachonline.com/2014/11/04/4584569_rice-declared-victor-in-bid-for.html?sp=/99/134/142/254/&rh=1|publisher=The Sun News|accessdate=8 November 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108061318/http://www.myrtlebeachonline.com/2014/11/04/4584569_rice-declared-victor-in-bid-for.html?sp=%2F99%2F134%2F142%2F254%2F&rh=1|archivedate=2014年11月8日}}</ref>。
